    Add changelog race condition test
    
    Add a Postgres-only integration test that reproduces the changelog
    cursor skip bug (#11087 / PR #3904) using the real
    AssignRequisitionNumber processor. The test inserts three requisitions
    with a deliberately delayed middle transaction, then verifies all
    three are processed. Removing the LOCK TABLE statement causes the
    test to fail, confirming it catches the race condition.

